documentation.text:
@dev Returns the farm address and liquidity pool address for each available farm on Ubeswap
 @return address[] memory The farm address for each available farm

attributes.text:
@dev Returns the farm address and liquidity pool address for each available farm on Ubeswap
 @return address[] memory The farm address for each available farm

addLiquidity(address,address,uint256,uin.details: Adds liquidity for the two given tokens; meant to be called from a pool

returns._0: uint The number of tokens LP tokens minted

checkIfFarmExists(address).details: Given the address of a farm on Ubeswap, returns the farm's staking token address

params.farmAddress: Address of the farm to check

returns._0: address The farm's staking token address

getAmountsOut(uint256,address,address).details: Given an input asset amount, returns the maximum output amount of the other asset

params.currencyKeyIn: Address of the asset to be swap from
params.currencyKeyOut: Address of the asset to be swap to

returns._0: uint Amount out of the asset

getAvailableRewards(address,address).details: Returns the amount of UBE rewards available for the pool in the given farm

params.farmAddress: Address of the farm on Ubeswap

getAvailableUbeswapFarms().details: Returns the farm address and liquidity pool address for each available farm on Ubeswap

returns._0: address[] memory The farm address for each available farm

getPair(address,address).details: Returns the address of a token pair

getPrice(address).details: Given an input asset address, returns the price of the asset in cUSD

getTokenAmountsFromPair(address,address,.details: Calculates the amount of tokens in a pair

params.numberOfLPTokens: Number of LP tokens for the given pair

returns._0: (uint, uint) The number of tokens for tokenA and tokenB

removeLiquidity(address,address,uint256).details: Removes liquidity for the two given tokens; meant to be called from a pool

params.numberOfLPTokens: Number of LP tokens for the given pair

returns._0: (uint, uint) Amount of tokenA and tokenB withdrawn

swapFromBot(address,address,uint256,uint.details: Swaps an exact `amountToSwap` of an asset to another; meant to be called from a trading bot

params.amountToSwap: Exact amount of `assetToSwapFrom` to be swapped
params.minAmountOut: the min amount of `assetToSwapTo` to be received from the swap

returns._0: uint The number of tokens received

swapFromPool(address,address,uint256,uin.details: Swaps an exact `amountToSwap` of an asset to another; meant to be called from a user pool

params.amountToSwap: Exact amount of `assetToSwapFrom` to be swapped
params.minAmountOut: the min amount of `assetToSwapTo` to be received from the swap

returns._0: uint The number of tokens received
